# Solvio booking

When editing matched files, read and follow:

- `.cursor/skills/solvio-booking/SKILL.md`
- `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-19-solvio-booking-domain-design.md`

Hard rules: no table bookings on upcoming show nights; event nights use purple calendar; cancel nights via `cancelled_occurrences` with optional guest-facing reason; validate on server in `actions.ts`.
